{"name": "Reynoldsburg Helping Hands", "alternate_name": "", "description": "Eligibility: Reynoldsburg School District residents only. Clients may visit the pantry every other month.

Intake Process: Telephone for appointment. No walkins. Clients must call, leave a voicemail message and
then wait for a return call from the pantry.

Documents: Recent utility bill, mail or lease for adults. Children also need to be verified with some form of
ID.
